_:N23ad493060bd4c4db316fd7b24d29a1f <http://schema.org/name> "About us" .
_:N23ad493060bd4c4db316fd7b24d29a1f <http://schema.org/image> <https://www.gov.uk/assets/frontend/govuk_publishing_components/govuk-schema-placeholder-4x3-194fde4197f00e669f6f52c182df2ed707bfb2024c9ef39f7a2ed20da62b90eb.png> .
_:N23ad493060bd4c4db316fd7b24d29a1f <http://schema.org/description> "Our mission is to deliver a geological disposal facility and provide radioactive waste management solutions. We are engaging with communities to inform our work." .
_:N23ad493060bd4c4db316fd7b24d29a1f <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"our-commitment\">Our commitment</h2>\n\n<p>RWM is engaging in discussions to help build understanding of geological disposal and the process to identify a site for a UK geological disposal facility.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"who-we-are\">Who we are</h2>\n\n<p>We are a wholly-owned subsidiary of the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/nuclear-decommissioning-authority\">Nuclear Decommissioning Authority (<abbr title=\"Nuclear Decommissioning Authority\">NDA</abbr>)</a>, which is an Executive Non-Departmental Public Body of the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-business-energy-and-industrial-strategy\">Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy (BEIS)</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"our-objectives\">Our objectives</h2>\n\n<p>Our 2020-21 key activities are:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>Implement government policy on geological disposal of higher activity waste</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Work proactively with waste producers to plan for and deliver waste management solutions</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Deliver a robust Technical Programme to support the GDF programme and waste management</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Develop RWM into a high performing delivery organisation</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/916520/RWM_Annual_Review_2019_20_English.pdf\">Read more.</a></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"our-strategies-and-corporate-reports\">Our strategies and corporate reports</h2>\n\n<p><span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5f5a2c17d3bf7f7237cf3e82/A_Permanent_Solution_for_Higher_-_Activity_Radioactive_Waste.pdf\">A Permanent Solution for Higher-Activity Radioactive Waste</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">5.94 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">11 pages</span>)</span> sets out the importance of taking responsibility for and dealing with the UK’s higher-activity radioactive waste as the right thing to do for future generations. It explains our approach for delivering a Geological Disposal Facility (GDF) in the UK.</p>\n\n<section data-module=\"ga4-link-tracker\" class=\"gem-c-attachment govuk-!-margin-bottom-6\">\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail govuk-!-display-none-print\">\n    <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5f5a2c17d3bf7f7237cf3e82/A_Permanent_Solution_for_Higher_-_Activity_Radioactive_Waste.pdf\">\n        <svg class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image--pdf\" version=\"1.1\" viewbox=\"0 0 99 140\">\n  <path d=\"M12,59h9v9h-9v-9ZM30,77v9h39v-9H30ZM30,104h57v-9H30v9ZM30,122h48v-9H30v9ZM12,86h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,122h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,104h9v-9h-9v9ZM30,68h57v-9H30v9ZM35.2,21c-.3-.2-.6-.4-1-.5s-.8-.2-1.3-.2h-2.6v5.5h2.6c.5,0,1,0,1.3-.2s.7-.3,1-.5c.3-.2.5-.5.7-.8s.2-.7.2-1.1h0c0-.5,0-.9-.2-1.2-.2-.3-.4-.6-.7-.8h0ZM52.4,21.9c-.4-.5-1-.9-1.6-1.1-.7-.3-1.5-.4-2.4-.4h-2.7v11.5h2.7c.9,0,1.7-.1,2.4-.4s1.2-.7,1.6-1.1c.4-.5.7-1.1.9-1.7.2-.7.3-1.4.3-2.1v-.7c0-.8,0-1.5-.3-2.1-.2-.6-.5-1.2-.9-1.7h0ZM87,12v27H12V12h75ZM39.8,23c0-.9-.1-1.6-.4-2.4-.3-.7-.7-1.4-1.2-1.9-.5-.5-1.2-1-1.9-1.2-.8-.3-1.6-.5-2.5-.5h-7.2v17.9h3.6v-6h3.2c.9,0,1.8-.1,2.6-.5.8-.3,1.4-.7,2-1.2.5-.5,1-1.2,1.3-1.9.3-.7.5-1.5.5-2.4h0ZM57.4,26c0-1.3-.2-2.6-.5-3.7s-.9-2-1.6-2.8c-.7-.8-1.6-1.4-2.7-1.8-1.1-.4-2.3-.6-3.8-.6h-6.6v17.9h6.6c1.5,0,2.7-.2,3.8-.6,1.1-.4,2-1,2.7-1.8.7-.8,1.3-1.7,1.6-2.8.4-1.1.5-2.3.5-3.7h0ZM72.4,17.1h-12.1v17.9h3.6v-7.5h7.8v-3.3h-7.8v-3.8h8.4s0-3.3,0-3.3Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__details\">\n    <h2 class=\"gem-c-attachment__title\">\n      <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5f5a2c17d3bf7f7237cf3e82/A_Permanent_Solution_for_Higher_-_Activity_Radioactive_Waste.pdf\">A Permanent Solution for Higher-Activity Radioactive Waste</a>\n</h2>\n\n\n      <p class=\"gem-c-attachment__metadata\"><span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\">5.94 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\">11 pages</span></p>\n\n\n\n\n</div></section>\n\n<p>The report is also available in Welsh: <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5f57a9cbd3bf7f7237cf3e3c/A_Permanent_Solution_for_Higher_-_Activity_Radioactive_Waste_Welsh_Language.pdf\">A Permanent Solution for Higher Activity Radioactive Waste (Welsh Language)</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">5.98 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">11 pages</span>)</span></p>\n\n<p>We have published our <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60f92af1e90e0703b77c9b4c/RWM_AnnualReview_2020_21.pdf\">Annual Review 2020-21</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">14.5 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">23 pages</span>)</span>, which sets out progress on delivering RWM’s mission and plans for the future.</p>\n\n<p>Alongside this we have published an <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60f92b798fa8f5042bb97a33/RWM_AnnualReview_2020_21_SUMMARY_DIGITAL.pdf\">Annual Review 2020-21 Summary</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">6.95 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">12 pages</span>)</span>.</p>\n\n<section data-module=\"ga4-link-tracker\" class=\"gem-c-attachment govuk-!-margin-bottom-6\">\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail govuk-!-display-none-print\">\n    <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60f92af1e90e0703b77c9b4c/RWM_AnnualReview_2020_21.pdf\">\n        <svg class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image--pdf\" version=\"1.1\" viewbox=\"0 0 99 140\">\n  <path d=\"M12,59h9v9h-9v-9ZM30,77v9h39v-9H30ZM30,104h57v-9H30v9ZM30,122h48v-9H30v9ZM12,86h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,122h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,104h9v-9h-9v9ZM30,68h57v-9H30v9ZM35.2,21c-.3-.2-.6-.4-1-.5s-.8-.2-1.3-.2h-2.6v5.5h2.6c.5,0,1,0,1.3-.2s.7-.3,1-.5c.3-.2.5-.5.7-.8s.2-.7.2-1.1h0c0-.5,0-.9-.2-1.2-.2-.3-.4-.6-.7-.8h0ZM52.4,21.9c-.4-.5-1-.9-1.6-1.1-.7-.3-1.5-.4-2.4-.4h-2.7v11.5h2.7c.9,0,1.7-.1,2.4-.4s1.2-.7,1.6-1.1c.4-.5.7-1.1.9-1.7.2-.7.3-1.4.3-2.1v-.7c0-.8,0-1.5-.3-2.1-.2-.6-.5-1.2-.9-1.7h0ZM87,12v27H12V12h75ZM39.8,23c0-.9-.1-1.6-.4-2.4-.3-.7-.7-1.4-1.2-1.9-.5-.5-1.2-1-1.9-1.2-.8-.3-1.6-.5-2.5-.5h-7.2v17.9h3.6v-6h3.2c.9,0,1.8-.1,2.6-.5.8-.3,1.4-.7,2-1.2.5-.5,1-1.2,1.3-1.9.3-.7.5-1.5.5-2.4h0ZM57.4,26c0-1.3-.2-2.6-.5-3.7s-.9-2-1.6-2.8c-.7-.8-1.6-1.4-2.7-1.8-1.1-.4-2.3-.6-3.8-.6h-6.6v17.9h6.6c1.5,0,2.7-.2,3.8-.6,1.1-.4,2-1,2.7-1.8.7-.8,1.3-1.7,1.6-2.8.4-1.1.5-2.3.5-3.7h0ZM72.4,17.1h-12.1v17.9h3.6v-7.5h7.8v-3.3h-7.8v-3.8h8.4s0-3.3,0-3.3Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__details\">\n    <h2 class=\"gem-c-attachment__title\">\n      <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60f92af1e90e0703b77c9b4c/RWM_AnnualReview_2020_21.pdf\">Annual Review 2020-21</a>\n</h2>\n\n\n      <p class=\"gem-c-attachment__metadata\"><span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\">14.5 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\">23 pages</span></p>\n\n\n\n\n</div></section>\n\n<section data-module=\"ga4-link-tracker\" class=\"gem-c-attachment govuk-!-margin-bottom-6\">\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail govuk-!-display-none-print\">\n    <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60f92b798fa8f5042bb97a33/RWM_AnnualReview_2020_21_SUMMARY_DIGITAL.pdf\">\n        <svg class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image--pdf\" version=\"1.1\" viewbox=\"0 0 99 140\">\n  <path d=\"M12,59h9v9h-9v-9ZM30,77v9h39v-9H30ZM30,104h57v-9H30v9ZM30,122h48v-9H30v9ZM12,86h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,122h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,104h9v-9h-9v9ZM30,68h57v-9H30v9ZM35.2,21c-.3-.2-.6-.4-1-.5s-.8-.2-1.3-.2h-2.6v5.5h2.6c.5,0,1,0,1.3-.2s.7-.3,1-.5c.3-.2.5-.5.7-.8s.2-.7.2-1.1h0c0-.5,0-.9-.2-1.2-.2-.3-.4-.6-.7-.8h0ZM52.4,21.9c-.4-.5-1-.9-1.6-1.1-.7-.3-1.5-.4-2.4-.4h-2.7v11.5h2.7c.9,0,1.7-.1,2.4-.4s1.2-.7,1.6-1.1c.4-.5.7-1.1.9-1.7.2-.7.3-1.4.3-2.1v-.7c0-.8,0-1.5-.3-2.1-.2-.6-.5-1.2-.9-1.7h0ZM87,12v27H12V12h75ZM39.8,23c0-.9-.1-1.6-.4-2.4-.3-.7-.7-1.4-1.2-1.9-.5-.5-1.2-1-1.9-1.2-.8-.3-1.6-.5-2.5-.5h-7.2v17.9h3.6v-6h3.2c.9,0,1.8-.1,2.6-.5.8-.3,1.4-.7,2-1.2.5-.5,1-1.2,1.3-1.9.3-.7.5-1.5.5-2.4h0ZM57.4,26c0-1.3-.2-2.6-.5-3.7s-.9-2-1.6-2.8c-.7-.8-1.6-1.4-2.7-1.8-1.1-.4-2.3-.6-3.8-.6h-6.6v17.9h6.6c1.5,0,2.7-.2,3.8-.6,1.1-.4,2-1,2.7-1.8.7-.8,1.3-1.7,1.6-2.8.4-1.1.5-2.3.5-3.7h0ZM72.4,17.1h-12.1v17.9h3.6v-7.5h7.8v-3.3h-7.8v-3.8h8.4s0-3.3,0-3.3Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__details\">\n    <h2 class=\"gem-c-attachment__title\">\n      <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60f92b798fa8f5042bb97a33/RWM_AnnualReview_2020_21_SUMMARY_DIGITAL.pdf\">Annual Review 2020-21 Summary</a>\n</h2>\n\n\n      <p class=\"gem-c-attachment__metadata\"><span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\">6.95 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\">12 pages</span></p>\n\n\n\n\n</div></section>\n\n<p>We have also published our <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5f59cfd4d3bf7f723d08be58/RWM_Business_Plan_2020_23_Annex.pdf\">Business Plan 2020-23 Annex</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">3.19 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">11 pages</span>)</span>.</p>\n\n<section data-module=\"ga4-link-tracker\" class=\"gem-c-attachment govuk-!-margin-bottom-6\">\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail govuk-!-display-none-print\">\n    <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5f59cfd4d3bf7f723d08be58/RWM_Business_Plan_2020_23_Annex.pdf\">\n        <svg class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image--pdf\" version=\"1.1\" viewbox=\"0 0 99 140\">\n  <path d=\"M12,59h9v9h-9v-9ZM30,77v9h39v-9H30ZM30,104h57v-9H30v9ZM30,122h48v-9H30v9ZM12,86h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,122h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,104h9v-9h-9v9ZM30,68h57v-9H30v9ZM35.2,21c-.3-.2-.6-.4-1-.5s-.8-.2-1.3-.2h-2.6v5.5h2.6c.5,0,1,0,1.3-.2s.7-.3,1-.5c.3-.2.5-.5.7-.8s.2-.7.2-1.1h0c0-.5,0-.9-.2-1.2-.2-.3-.4-.6-.7-.8h0ZM52.4,21.9c-.4-.5-1-.9-1.6-1.1-.7-.3-1.5-.4-2.4-.4h-2.7v11.5h2.7c.9,0,1.7-.1,2.4-.4s1.2-.7,1.6-1.1c.4-.5.7-1.1.9-1.7.2-.7.3-1.4.3-2.1v-.7c0-.8,0-1.5-.3-2.1-.2-.6-.5-1.2-.9-1.7h0ZM87,12v27H12V12h75ZM39.8,23c0-.9-.1-1.6-.4-2.4-.3-.7-.7-1.4-1.2-1.9-.5-.5-1.2-1-1.9-1.2-.8-.3-1.6-.5-2.5-.5h-7.2v17.9h3.6v-6h3.2c.9,0,1.8-.1,2.6-.5.8-.3,1.4-.7,2-1.2.5-.5,1-1.2,1.3-1.9.3-.7.5-1.5.5-2.4h0ZM57.4,26c0-1.3-.2-2.6-.5-3.7s-.9-2-1.6-2.8c-.7-.8-1.6-1.4-2.7-1.8-1.1-.4-2.3-.6-3.8-.6h-6.6v17.9h6.6c1.5,0,2.7-.2,3.8-.6,1.1-.4,2-1,2.7-1.8.7-.8,1.3-1.7,1.6-2.8.4-1.1.5-2.3.5-3.7h0ZM72.4,17.1h-12.1v17.9h3.6v-7.5h7.8v-3.3h-7.8v-3.8h8.4s0-3.3,0-3.3Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__details\">\n    <h2 class=\"gem-c-attachment__title\">\n      <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5f59cfd4d3bf7f723d08be58/RWM_Business_Plan_2020_23_Annex.pdf\">Business Plan 2020-23 Annex</a>\n</h2>\n\n\n      <p class=\"gem-c-attachment__metadata\"><span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\">3.19 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\">11 pages</span></p>\n\n\n\n\n</div></section>\n\n<p>This report is also available in Welsh: <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5f58989be90e071462cf702f/RWM_BusinessPlan_2020_23_Annex_WELSH.pdf\">Business Plan 2020-23 Annex (Welsh Language)</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">3.07 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">11 pages</span>)</span></p>\n\n<p>Previous Annual Review: <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5f59cfc1e90e071464d1d318/RWM_Annual_Review_2019_20_English.pdf\">Annual Review 2019-20</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">6.29 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">24 pages</span>)</span></p>\n\n<p>Previous Annual Review in Welsh: <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5f5896128fa8f5106b23a9d1/RWM_Annual_Review_2019_20_Welsh.pdf\">Annual Review 2019-20 (Welsh Language)</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">6.26 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">24 pages</span>)</span></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"information-for-communities\">Information for communities</h2>\n\n<p>In support of Government policy on geological disposal, RWM has published information for communities including:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/835825/RWM_Prospectus_EnglandV1_a.pdf\">Introduction to Geological Disposal</a> - An overview into our mission to deal with radioactive waste</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/835826/RWM_CommunityGuidance_ENGLAND_a.pdf\">Community Guidance</a> - How we will work with communities</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/866403/RWM_Site_Evaluation_for_England_2020.pdf\">Site Evaluation</a> - How we will evaluate sites in England.</li>\n  <li>\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/about-national-geological-screening-ngs\">National Geological Screening for a GDF</a>. A high level summary of the geological information which is relevant to the safety of a GDF.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/the-siting-process-for-a-geological-disposal-facility-gdf\">Read more.</a></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"issues-management\">Issues management</h2>\n\n<p>If you have an issue that you would like to raise that relates to implementing geological disposal. See our <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://rwm.nda.gov.uk/issues/\">issues register</a></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"technical-reports\">Technical reports</h2>\n\n<p>While RWM corporate reports are available on this website, some technical publications and commissioned research prepared by third parties are available from our <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://rwm.nda.gov.uk/publications/\">document library</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"archive-materials\">Archive materials</h2>\n<p>All content from our previous website, published prior to joining GOV.UK, is available in <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20150717155707/http:/www.nda.gov.uk/rwm\">The National Archive</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"contacting-us\">Contacting us</h2>\n<p>To contact us about any aspects of our work, email us at <a href=\"mailto:gdfenquiries@nda.gov.uk\">gdfenquiries@nda.gov.uk</a></p>\n\n</div>" .
